summary: Retextures of Tom349s claw, katar, perforator and punching dagger.
descriptionHtml:
Simple higher quality retextures of Tom349s claw, katar, perforator and punching dagger.

Requires original mod by Tom349: [url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/downloads/file.php?id=7552]Found Here[/url]
Additional retextures by Bloodysunday: [url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/downloads/file.php?id=7752]Found Here[/url]

To use mine with Bloodysunday\'s textures for the other weapons just install his first then overwrite with mine.

Don\'t mind the blurring in the pictures, it\'s from depth of field that I was too lazy to shut off.  Be sure to endorse Tom349s mod for providing quality fist weapons.
author: Palderon
